        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">How Our Technology Works</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Our AI-powered platform uses advanced algorithms to analyze resumes and match them with job descriptions.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
